msgid "命令执行"
msgstr "Command Execution"

#: ../../source/language/javascript/misc.rst:6
msgid "Node.js中child_process.exec命令调用的是 ``/bin/sh`` ，故可以直接使用该命令执行shell"
msgstr "In Node.js, the child_process.exec command invokes ``/bin/sh``, so this command can be used directly to execute shell commands."

